Olive Ann Alcorn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olive_Ann_Alcorn 0 Olive Ann Alcorn (October 2, 1900 – January 8, 1975) was an American dancer, model, and silent film actress of the 1910s and 1920s. She is better remembered today for the numerous nude photographs of her from the era than for her film work.
